ygData.messageBody:
Greetings,
I am a lvl 12, almost 13 Ranger/woodelf who is in need of guidance to
where i can up my lvls. I have been residing in North Quynos and am
getting bored with the scenery. I have a good weapon but it isn't
hitting for as many points as i would like, typical story huh?
I am confusted about the quests, how do you learn about them?
I went through one for a sword, but when i finished and got my prize
it was only for human rangers and high elf rangers, i was
devistated!!! All that work and no show for it.
Anways, any help/hints/ideas would be greatly appriciated!!!
-Melefante
